OL,3,CTwo-week long bus strikes called off
OL,4,Cas drivers accept pay offer
OL,6,FStrikes by six hundred First Bus
OL,7,Fdrivers over the first two weeks of
OL,8,FOctober have been called off, after
OL,9,Fworkers accepted a new pay deal.
OL,11,FThe staff from two depots, Lawrence
OL,12,FHill and Hengrove, walked out for four
OL,13,Fdays last month causing mass
OL,14,Fdisruption across Bristol. They had
OL,15,Fbeen planning further strike action.
OL,17,FBut the Unite union says following
OL,18,Fnegotiations, members have voted to
OL,19,Faccept the new offer.
