OL,3,CTwo-week long bus strikes called off
OL,4,Cas drivers accept pay offer
OL,6,FDrivers will receive an increase from
OL,7,F#16 an hour to #16.50 backdated to 1
OL,8,FApril. This goes up to #17 an hour
OL,9,Fbackdated to 28 September. Workers
OL,10,Fwill then have another rise to #17.40
OL,11,Fan hour from 1 April 2026.
OL,13,FThis works out as an 8.6 per cent pay
OL,14,Fincrease over two years.
