OL,3,CTwo-week long bus strikes called off
OL,4,Cas drivers accept pay offer
OL,6,FA major source of contention
OL,7,Fthroughout the pay dispute was First
OL,8,FWest of England not committing to
OL,9,Fpaying drivers backpay. To address
OL,10,Fthis, workers at the City Line will
OL,11,Fget #250 non-consolidated backpay and
OL,12,Ftheir rest day working has gone up by
OL,13,F50p to #1.51 per hour.
OL,15,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,16,Fsaid: "Bus drivers do a difficult,
OL,17,Fimportant job for the general public
OL,18,Fand deserve to be paid appropriately.
