OL,6,F"This is a fantastic win for workers
OL,7,Fat First West of England, who stuck
OL,8,Ffirmly together throughout the
OL,9,Findustrial action to get the pay offer
OL,10,Fthey deserved. It is yet more proof
OL,11,Fthat there is power in a union."
OL,13,FUnite regional officer Amy Roberts
OL,14,Fadded: "We are very pleased with the
OL,15,Foutcome of this industrial action, as
OL,16,Fit has led to a fantastic new deal for
OL,17,Fthe bus drivers, who do a very hard
OL,18,Fjob.
